---
import SiteHeader from './SiteHeader.astro';
import { site } from '../content/site';
---

<footer class="border-t border-[var(--color-rule)] bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-12">
    <div class="mb-10 flex flex-col gap-8 md:flex-row md:justify-between">
      <div>
        <SiteHeader size="sm" />
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-ink-2)]">
          출장 청소업체를 위한 예약·일정·고객 관리 모바일 앱
        </p>
      </div>
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm font-medium">
        <a href="/#features">기능</a>
        <a href="/#how">사용 방법</a>
        <a href="/#contact">상담</a>
        <a href="/terms">이용약관</a>
        <a href="/privacy">개인정보처리방침</a>
        <a href="/delete-account">계정 삭제 요청</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-[var(--color-rule)] pt-6 text-xs leading-relaxed text-[var(--color-muted)]">
      <p class="mb-2 font-medium text-[var(--color-ink-2)]">사업자 정보</p>
      <p>
        {site.companyName} · 대표 {site.representative} · 사업자등록번호 {site.businessNumber}
      </p>
      <p>{site.address}</p>
      <p class="mt-1">
        <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">{site.email}</a>
        {' · '}
        <a href={`tel:${site.phone.replace(/-/g, '')}`} class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">{site.phone}</a>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        © {new Date().getFullYear()} {site.companyName}. {site.serviceName} 서비스.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
